      "widgets_values": [
        "QUICK PANEL \u00b7 FLUX SCHNELL\n\nMODELS (split weights):\n  #1  diffusion_models/flux1-schnell.safetensors  (download: Comfy-Org/flux_schnell on HF)\n  #23 text_encoders/clip_l.safetensors + t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors  (DualCLIPLoader type: flux)\n  #24 vae/ae.safetensors  (same Flux AE used by Z-Image Turbo)\n\n\u26a0\ufe0f  FIRST RUN \u2014 REQUIRED INIT IMAGE:\n  Flux's VAE outputs 16-channel latents; DeforumSingleSampleNode's cold-start path hardcodes 4 channels.\n  Fix: always provide an init image so the VAE-encode path is used instead.\n  Place ANY 1024\u00d7576 PNG at  ComfyUI/input/flux_schnell_continue.png  before the first queue.\n  After each run, #28 (WAS save, unmute+configure) auto-overwrites it with the last frame\n  \u2014 enabling seamless continuation with no manual steps.\n\nFLUX SCHNELL SETTINGS:\n  Sampler: euler  |  Scheduler: simple  |  Steps: 4 (hard limit \u2014 more steps degrade quality)\n  CFG: 1.0 flat (distilled; negative prompts have no effect at CFG=1)\n  Strength: eased 0.50\u21920.38\u21920.50  |  Noise: ~0.014\u20130.026 (ultra-low for temporal coherence)\n\nPERFORMANCE:  fp8 loaders \u2192 set #1 UNETLoader dtype to fp8_e4m3fn_fast on Ada/Hopper GPUs.\n\nALTERNATIVE ANIM NODES (row below, disabled): #25 Depth \u00b7 #26 Cadence \u00b7 #27 Color\nCONTROLNET (bottom-right, muted): see Note #31 \u2014 iterator+KSampler path required."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
